
Basic Build
------------------

Three ways to build: (1) meson [preferable], (2) cmake, (3) pure make [last resort]

(1) meson
meson setup _build
meson compile -C _build
# meson install -C _build

(2) cmake
cmake -B _build -S $(pwd)
cmake --build _build
# cmake --install _build

(3) make
make
# make install


Package Templates
------------------

Template samples are located in
